---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Nitrous Oxide Sedation Lethbridge | Able Family Dental"
  description="Nitrous oxide (laughing gas) sedation at Able Family Dental in Lethbridge. A safe, mild option for children and adults with dental anxiety. Dr. Tyler Snow certified."
>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[42%] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        src="/images/services/hero-nitrous-oxide.jpg"
        alt=""
        width="800"
        height="600"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-2/3" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-brand-primary), transparent);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-wide relative py-16 lg:py-24 lg:max-w-[64%]">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] mb-5" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Services</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/sedation/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Sedation</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="text-white">Nitrous Oxide</span>
      </nav>
      <p class="eyebrow text-white">Sedation Dentistry</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-5xl)] leading-tight text-white max-w-2xl">
        Nitrous Oxide (Laughing Gas)
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        A gentle, time-tested sedation option that helps you relax during dental treatment — and wears off completely within minutes of the appointment ending.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CONTENT
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section-y bg-[var(--color-surface-cool)]">
    <div class="container-wide">

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-14">
        <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] leading-tight text-[var(--color-brand-primary)]">
          Calm, comfortable, and in control
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Nitrous oxide — commonly known as laughing gas — is a safe, colourless gas that you breathe in through a small, comfortable mask placed over your nose. Within a few minutes you will feel a pleasant sense of warmth and relaxation. You remain fully conscious, can hear and respond to Dr. Snow throughout your appointment, and stay in complete control at all times.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-14">

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Fast-acting relief</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Nitrous oxide takes effect within minutes of breathing it in. Your dentist can also adjust the level of sedation throughout the procedure to keep you comfortable from start to finish.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Wears off quickly</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Once the mask is removed and you breathe regular air for a few minutes, the effects of nitrous oxide dissipate completely. Most patients can drive themselves home and return to normal activities right away.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Suitable for all ages</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Nitrous oxide is one of the safest sedation options available and is well-suited for both children and adults. It is particularly helpful for patients with mild dental anxiety, a sensitive gag reflex, or those undergoing longer procedures.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Detail section -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md">
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Is nitrous oxide right for you?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Dr. Tyler Snow is certified in nitrous oxide sedation and will review your health history and anxiety level during your consultation to determine whether it is a good fit. Nitrous oxide is generally recommended for patients who:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
          {[
            "Experience mild to moderate dental anxiety",
            "Have a sensitive gag reflex that makes treatment difficult",
            "Are children or adults who feel nervous about dental visits",
            "Need to remain alert after their appointment",
            "Are undergoing routine procedures such as fillings, cleanings, or extractions",
          ].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[var(--color-brand-accent)]" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-sm">
          If you have more significant anxiety or are facing a complex procedure, Dr. Snow may recommend oral sedation or IV sedation for a deeper level of comfort. <a href="/services/sedation/" class="text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] font-semibold hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-hover)] transition-colors">Explore all sedation options →</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CTA BAND
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] py-16 text-center overflow-hidden relative">
    <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none" viewBox="0 0 1440 160" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M0 60 C 240 20, 480 100, 720 60 C 960 20, 1200 100, 1440 60 L1440 160 L0 160 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="relative container-wide">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] text-white leading-tight">Ready to feel comfortable at the dentist?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Call <a href="tel:+14033277202" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-soft)] transition-colors">403.327.7202</a> or request an appointment online.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/book/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Request an Appointment</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-lg border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
